getInstanceId

int getInstanceId()
Returns the instance id. Note that instance IDs are 1-based. When not running in a GSC, defaults to 1.

Returns:
the instance id.

getHostAddress

String getHostAddress()
Returns the host address. When not running in a GSC, default to the local host address.

Returns:
the host address.

getHostName

String getHostName()
Returns the host name. When not running in a GSC, default to the local host name.

Returns:
the host name.

getDetails

Object getDetails(String serviceDetailsKey)
Returns the details for the given key by iterating over all service details in this processing unit instances and returning the first match.

serviceDetailsKey - the details key.
Returns:
the details result, which may be null if the key does not exist in the service details.
